# Demon Slayer Game

A text-based Demon Slayer game written in Python.

## How to Play

1. Clone or download the repository.
2. Make sure you have Python installed.
3. Run the game.py script.
4. Follow the on-screen instructions to play.

## Game Controls

- Enter 'attack' to attack the demon.
- Follow on-screen instructions for other actions.

## Dependencies

- Python 3.x

